messages.title: Dear Voter,
messages.content: This is a critical General Election for Britain, and your vote will shape its future.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: For 27 years, UKIP has fought for a Clean-Break Brexit. Only a vote for UKIP is a vote to honour the Referendum result.

issues.brexitEurope: UKIP has fought for a Clean-Break Brexit. Vote UKIP to send a message to our liar politicians that they will never forget.
issues.governance: Establishment politicians in Westminster have been busy betraying us, reneging on their 2017 manifesto promises.
issues.immigration: Labour wants a second referendum and open-door immigration. The Libdems would revoke Article 50, to lock us into the EU forever.

images.caption: David Moreland, UKIP Candidate for Norwich North

leaflet.additionalNotes: Please note that certain details, such as the election date, contact information, personal statements, political experience, endorsements, and quotes are not available from the provided image of the campaign leaflet.
